Developed by JuniorCloud LLC, this edge-native compiler bypasses heavy server frameworks to translate high-dimensional dense continuous model manifolds (FP16/BF16) into strict discrete operational matrices (b1.58 and b1.0) targeting Apple's Matrix Coprocessor (AMX).\
